<div class="wrap1 -pt:3">		<div class="wrap1-contain -xw:1"><section class="article-info">
<div class="article-content">
<div class="article-body">
<h1>Giving facts a fighting chance</h1>
<p>As part of a comprehensive effort to combat misinformation about COVID-19 and the strain of coronavirus (SARS-CoV-2) that causes it, NLP created this resource page to provide accurate information about the pandemic.</p>
<p>It includes free resources for educators, students and the general public, along with links to authoritative sources of health information. You&#8217;ll also find tips, tools and quizzes to build news literacy skills that will last long after this public health crisis abates.</p>
<p>We are refreshing the content of this page periodically. Follow us on social media for timely updates.</p>
<p class="socials" style="text-align: left;"><a style="text-decoration: none; color: transparent;" href="https://facebook.com/TheNewsLiteracyProject/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img style="width: 40px;" data-src="https://newslit.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/fb_20.svg" class="lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" /><noscript><img style="width: 40px;" src="https://newslit.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/fb_20.svg" /></noscript> </a><a style="text-decoration: none; color: transparent;" href="https://twitter.com/NewsLitProject/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img style="width: 40px;" data-src="https://newslit.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Twitter_20.svg" class="lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" /><noscript><img style="width: 40px;" src="https://newslit.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Twitter_20.svg" /></noscript> </a><a style="text-decoration: none; color: transparent;" href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/the-news-literacy-project/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img style="width: 40px;" data-src="https://newslit.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/LI_20.svg" class="lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" /><noscript><img style="width: 40px;" src="https://newslit.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/LI_20.svg" /></noscript> </a><a style="text-decoration: none; color: transparent;" href="https://instagram.com/NewsLitProject/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img style="width: 40px;" data-src="https://newslit.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Insta_20.svg" class="lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" /><noscript><img style="width: 40px;" src="https://newslit.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Insta_20.svg" /></noscript> </a><a style="text-decoration: none; color: transparent;" href="https://flipboard.com/@NewsLitProject/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img style="width