<li><a href="https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/index.html?emci=cb049f03-d167-ea11-a94c-00155d03b5dd&amp;emdi=c4ea6159-f467-ea11-a94c-00155d03b5dd&amp;ceid=3573302" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Centers for Disease Control and Prevention.</a></li>
<li><a href="https://coronavirus.jhu.edu/map.html?emci=cb049f03-d167-ea11-a94c-00155d03b5dd&amp;emdi=c4ea6159-f467-ea11-a94c-00155d03b5dd&amp;ceid=3573302" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Johns Hopkins University &amp; Medicine.</a></li>
<li><a href="https://covid19.fas.org/l/en?emci=cb049f03-d167-ea11-a94c-00155d03b5dd&amp;emdi=c4ea6159-f467-ea11-a94c-00155d03b5dd&amp;ceid=3573302" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Federation of American Scientists.</a></li>
